## 6.4. Add Reference Line

We can use `statline` to add a reference line. In this example, we use mean as the reference line.


::: {.cell}

```{.r .cell-code}
reactable(sales,
          defaultPageSize = 13,
          columns = 
            list(Product = colDef(maxWidth = 200),
            `Monthly Sales` = 
              colDef(cell = 
                       react_sparkline(sales,
                                       highlight_points =
                                         highlight_points(
                                           min = "red", max = "blue"),
                                       statline = "mean")))
            )
```

