## 6.5. Add Bandline

We can use the `bandline` argument to add bandlines:


::: {.cell}

```{.r .cell-code}
reactable(sales,
          defaultPageSize = 13,
          columns = 
            list(Product = colDef(maxWidth = 200),
            `Monthly Sales` = 
              colDef(cell = 
                       react_sparkline(sales,
                                       highlight_points =
                                         highlight_points(
                                           min = "red", max = "blue"),
                                       line_width = 1,
                                       bandline = "innerquartiles",
                                       bandline_color = "green")))
            )
```

