## 6.6. Changing Sparkline to Sparkbar


::: {.cell}

```{.r .cell-code}
reactable(sales,
          defaultPageSize = 13,
          columns = 
            list(Product = colDef(maxWidth = 200),
            `Monthly Sales` = 
              colDef(cell = 
                       react_sparkbar(sales,
                                      highlight_bars =
                                        highlight_bars(
                                          min = "red", max = "blue"),
                                      bandline = "innerquartiles",
                                      statline = "mean")))
            )
```

